---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const documents = [
  {
    title: 'Mutual NDA',
    description: 'A standard mutual non-disclosure agreement. We sign this before any commercial detail changes hands so you can speak freely about your business, roadmap and competitive position.',
    notice: 'If you would prefer a fully executed copy on file, please return a signed version by email prior to our scheduled meeting. Otherwise, by continuing our discussions, both parties shall be deemed to have accepted the terms set out in this NDA.',
    filename: 'mutual-nda.pdf',
    href: '/client-pack/mutual-nda.pdf',
    size: '12 KB',
    pages: null,
    order: '01',
  },
  {
    title: 'Capability Showcase',
    description: 'Selected case studies, what we have built, the stack we used and the outcomes we delivered. The single document to read if you want a feel for the calibre of work.',
    filename: 'awl-capability-showcase.pdf',
    href: '/client-pack/awl-capability-showcase.pdf',
    size: '149 KB',
    pages: null,
    order: '02',
  },
  {
    title: 'How This Works',
    description: 'Our engagement process from first call to handover, discovery, scoping, build cadence, quality gates and what we hand over at the end. Read this if you want to know exactly what working with us looks like.',
    filename: 'how-this-works.pdf',
    href: '/client-pack/how-this-works.pdf',
    size: '10 KB',
    pages: null,
    order: '03',
  },
];
---

<Layout
  title="How We Work, Capability Showcase, Process & NDA | All Webbed Labs"
  description="Download our capability showcase, engagement process document and mutual NDA. Everything we share with prospective clients after a discovery call."
  noindex={true}
>
  <Header />
  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hwk-hero">
      <div class="hwk-hero-inner">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Client Resources</span>
          <h1 class="hwk-title">
            Everything we send<br />
            <span class="gradient-text">after a discovery call.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hwk-lead">
            Three documents you would normally receive by email, published here so you can grab them whenever you need them, share them internally and reference them while we scope your engagement.
          </p>
          <p class="hwk-sub">
            If you have already spoken with us, this is the pack we promised to send through. If you have not, the documents below give a clear picture of what we build, how we work and the terms we operate under.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Documents -->
    <section class="docs-section">
      <div class="docs-inner">
        <div class="docs-list">
          {documents.map((doc, i) => (
            <article class={`doc-card reveal stagger-${i + 1}`}>
              <div class="doc-order">{doc.order}</div>
              <div class="doc-body">
                <div class="doc-meta">
                  <svg class="doc-pdf-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
                    <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="doc-type">PDF</span>
                  <span class="doc-divider">·</span>
                  <span class="doc-size">{doc.size}</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="doc-title">{doc.title}</h2>
                <p class="doc-description">{doc.description}</p>
                <div class="doc-actions">
                  <a href={doc.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary doc-btn">
                    Open PDF
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H8M17 7v9"/></svg>
                  </a>
                  <a href={doc.href} download={doc.filename} class="doc-btn-secondary">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
                    Download
                  </a>
                </div>
                {doc.notice && (
                  <p class="doc-notice">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                    <span>{doc.notice}</span>
                  </p>
                )}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What happens next -->
    <section class="next-section">
      <div class="next-inner">
        <div class="next-grid">
          <div class="reveal-left">
            <span class="section-label">What Happens Next</span>
            <h2 class="section-heading">The Path from Here to Signed</h2>
            <p>If the capability showcase and process document hold up to your standards, the next step is a working session. We use it to translate your brief into a concrete scope, a fixed timeline and an honest price.</p>
            <p>Before that session, we sign the mutual NDA so you can share anything material to the conversation, roadmaps, competitive context, internal politics, the parts of the problem your team has already tried.</p>
            <p>From a signed NDA to a costed proposal is typically five to ten working days, depending on how much surface area we need to map.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="next-steps reveal-right stagger-2">
            <div class="next-step">
              <div class="ns-num">1</div>
              <div class="ns-body">
                <strong>Read the pack</strong>
                <span>Capability showcase, process doc, NDA. About fifteen minutes total.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="next-step">
              <div class="ns-num">2</div>
              <div class="ns-body">
                <strong>Sign the NDA</strong>
                <span>Mutual, no scope, no commitment, purely so we can talk freely.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="next-step">
              <div class="ns-num">3</div>
              <div class="ns-body">
                <strong>Scoping session</strong>
                <span>Sixty to ninety minutes. We turn your brief into a surface map and risk register.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="next-step">
              <div class="ns-num">4</div>
              <div class="ns-body">
                <strong>Costed proposal</strong>
                <span>Fixed price or time-and-materials, deliverables, milestones, payment schedule.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ask CTA -->
    <section class="ask-section">
      <div class="ask-inner">
        <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <span class="section-label">Questions on Past Work</span>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Want Detail on a Specific Project?</h2>
          <p class="ask-copy">The capability showcase covers the highlights. If you want the engineering decisions behind a particular project, a reference from a past client, or to talk to the lead engineer who delivered it, just ask. We would rather walk you through it directly than dress it up in marketing copy.</p>
          <div class="ask-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Call</a>
            <a href="mailto:labs@allwebbedup.com.au" class="btn-outline">Email Us Directly</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hwk-hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
    background: #0a0f0e;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hwk-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 60% 30%, rgba(13,147,115,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hwk-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hwk-title {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 6.5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 760px;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }
  .hwk-lead {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #cde0da;
    max-width: 720px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #0d9373;
    background: rgba(13,147,115,0.05);
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }
  .hwk-sub {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.9375rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
    color: #8aa09a;
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }

  /* Documents */
  .docs-section { padding: 6rem 0; background: #0f1614; }
  .docs-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
  .docs-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .doc-card {
    background: #0a0f0e;
    border: 1px solid #1e2d28;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.25rem 2.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    align-items: start;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .doc-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(13,147,115,0.35);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .doc-order {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0d9373;
    background: rgba(13,147,115,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(13,147,115,0.18);
    border-radius: 12px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .doc-body { min-width: 0; }

  .doc-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #4a6359;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .doc-pdf-icon { color: #0d9373; }
  .doc-divider { color: #2a3d35; }

  .doc-title {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.625rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 0.625rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .doc-description {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #8aa09a;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .doc-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .doc-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.125rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .doc-btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.125rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #cde0da;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #1e2d28;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .doc-btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: rgba(13,147,115,0.45);
    color: white;
    background: rgba(13,147,115,0.05);
  }

  .doc-notice {
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0;
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.28);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #fca5a5;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .doc-notice svg {
    color: #ef4444;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  /* Next */
  .next-section { padding: 7rem 0; background: #0a0f0e; }
  .next-inner { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
  .next-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .next-section p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #8aa09a;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .next-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 4.5rem;
  }
  .next-step {
    background: #0f1614;
    border: 1px solid #1e2d28;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .ns-num {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0d9373;
    background: rgba(13,147,115,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(13,147,115,0.2);
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .ns-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .ns-body strong {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
  }
  .ns-body span {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #4a6359;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Ask */
  .ask-section { padding: 7rem 0; background: #0f1614; }
  .ask-inner { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
  .ask-copy {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #8aa09a;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .ask-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .next-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .next-steps { margin-top: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .doc-card {
      padding: 1.75rem;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .doc-order {
      width: 56px;
    }
  }
</style>
